{
  "chapter": 53,
  "chapter_summary": "龙啸云请李寻欢到其府中密谈，两人围绕聪明与痛苦展开深层对话。龙啸云坦言内心积压多年的痛苦根源——李寻欢将心爱的林诗音让给他做妻子，而林诗音心中始终爱着李寻欢。龙啸云认为当男人知道妻子是别人让给的，这才是最大的痛苦与羞辱。他声明自己既不会杀李寻欢，也不能放他，因为李寻欢还有被利用的价值。李寻欢则指出兴云庄园中藏宝一事从头到尾就是个骗局。最后龙啸云表示要带李寻欢去见一个人。场景转至一处密室，室内有二人：一人站于桌前翻阅账册卷宗，精神永不松弛；另一人如枪杆般笔直站立，蚊叮不眨眼，全身麻木不知痛痒。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "一个人的名字也许会起错，但外号却是绝不会起错的，有的人明明其笨如牛，也可以起个名字叫聪明，但一人的外号若是疯子，他就一定是个疯子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "但一个人若是太聪明了，知道的事太多，也许慢慢就会变成个疯子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "因为到了那种时候，他就会觉得做了疯子就会变得快乐些，所以有些人最大的痛苦就是他明明想做疯子，却做不到。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "幸好我一向不是个聪明人，也永远不会有这种烦恼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "大哥……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "我心里一直有句话要说，却不知该不该说出来。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "无论如何，我们已是多年的朋友。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "不是朋友，是兄弟。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "我是个怎么样的人，大哥你也该早已明白。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "是——",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "那么，大哥你无论要我做什么，都该当面对我说明才是，只要我能做到的，我一定会去想法子做到。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我明白你的意思，可是……时间有时会改变许多事。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "我也知道大哥你对我有些误会……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "误会？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "是误会，完全是误会，但有些事，大哥你本不该误会我的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "但也有件事我绝没有误会。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "哪件事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我知道你这些年来一直都很痛苦。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "大多数人都有痛苦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "但你的痛苦比别人都深得多，也重得多。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "因为你将你最心爱的人，让给了别人做妻子。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "但你的痛苦还不够深，因为一个人若是肯牺牲自己，成全别人，他就会觉得自己很伟大，这种感觉就会将他的痛苦减轻。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "真正的痛苦是什么，也许你还不知道。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "也许……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "当一个男人知道他的妻子原来是别人让给他的，而且他的妻子一直还是在爱着那个人，这才是最大的痛苦！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "今天我说的话，本是不该说的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 151,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "每个人偶尔都会说出一些他不该说的活，否则他就不是人了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "今天我请你来，也不是为了要说这些话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你可知道我请你来是为了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你知道？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "你认为'兴云庄'园中真有藏宝？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "你认为我知道藏宝在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你应该知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "我这人一向有个毛病……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "毛病？什么毛病？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "我的毛病就是不该知道的事我全知道，该知道的我反而不知道。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "其实你也应该知道，这件事从头到尾就是个骗局……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我相信你，因为我知道你绝不会说谎。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "若说这世上还有一个我可以信任的人，那人就是你；若说这世上我还有一个朋友，那人也是你！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我说的任何话也许都是假的，但这句话却绝不是骗你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "我也相信你，因为……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你相信我，因为你知道你已没有被我利用的价值，我已不必再骗你，是不是？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你一定认为我会杀你？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "无论你怎么样做，我都不怪你。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "但我绝不会杀你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "不错，你当然知道，你一向很了解我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "因为我纵然杀了你，也挽不回她的心，只有令她更恨我。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "人生中本有些事是谁也无可奈何的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "无可奈何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我虽不杀你，也不能放你。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我要带你去见一个人，这人早就想见你了，你……你或许也很想见他。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 265
    }
  ],
  "new_entities": {
    "characters": [
      {
        "id": "char_fan_juan_zhi_ren",
        "name": "翻卷之人",
        "alias": [
          "桌前之人"
